hotels.name: Eka Hotel Nairobi
hotels.description: This modern hotel off the A104 is 6 km from the Kenyatta International Convention Centre and 11 km from Jomo Kenyatta International Airport.Contemporary rooms and suites feature free Wi-Fi and flat-screen TVs, as well as minibars, and tea and coffeemaking facilities. Airy upgraded suites add living areas.Complimentary perks include parking and a breakfast buffet. There are 2 restaurants and a bar, plus an outdoor pool and a fitness center.

hotels.name: Sarova Whitesands Beach Resort & Spa
hotels.description: Set on 10 hectares of tropical, beachfront landscape, this high-end resort is 11 minutes' walk from Jomo Kenyatta Public Beach and 10 km from the Mombasa city centre.Relaxed rooms offer free Wi-Fi, flat-screen TVs and minibars, plus mosquito nets and balconies with sea and/or pool views. Refined suites add living areas, while upgraded quarters add kitchenettes, whirlpool baths and/or butler service.Breakfast is free. There are 5 outdoor pools, a diving school and a hot tub with sea views, plus a gym and a water sports centre. There are also 2 airy restaurants, 1 inside a bright pavilion, plus a stylish cafe, a beachfront bar and a nightclub.

hotels.name: Four Points by Sheraton Nairobi Hurlingham
hotels.description: This upscale hotel in Nairobi's Hurlingham Estate is a 7-minute walk from the Hurlingham Shopping Centre, 5.5 km from Nairobi National Museum and 13.2 km from Nairobi National Park.Contemporary rooms offer free WiFi and flat-screen TVs, plus desks, minibars and coffeemakers. Upgraded rooms feature balconies (some with mountain views), while suites add living areas with pull-out sofas. Room service is available 24/7.Freebies include parking and hot breakfast. There’s a modern international restaurant, an outdoor Arabic restaurant and a hip bar with city views, as well as a rooftop pool, a fitness center, 4 meeting rooms and a sundry store.

hotels.name: Fairview Hotel Nairobi
hotels.description: Set on 2 hectares of leafy grounds, this relaxed hotel lies 3 km from the Nairobi National Museum and 18 km from Jomo Kenyatta International Airport.Streamlined rooms feature flat-screen TVs, Wi-Fi and safes, as well as tea and coffeemaking facilities. Suites add kitchenettes; some offer private garden access. Room service is available.There’s an outdoor pool surrounded by lush gardens. Other amenities include 4 restaurants, plus a wine bar and a gym. Secured parking is available.

hotels.name: CityBlue Creekside Hotel & Suites
hotels.description: Off the B8 road, this colonial-style hotel overlooking the Tudor Creek estuary is a 13-minute walk from the Nyali Bridge. The 16th-century Fort Jesus is 5 km away.Featuring free Wi-Fi, the down-to-earth rooms have 4-poster beds with mosquito nets, plus flat-screen TVs and minifridges. They also come with balconies offering garden or estuary views. Airy suites add separate living areas and additional balconies, plus kitchenettes and dining spaces.Amenities include a restaurant, as well as an open-air bar set beside an outdoor pool. There's also a sundeck overlooking the estuary, along with a fitness center and a garden.

hotels.name: Sarova Panafric Hotel
hotels.description: Set on a hillside, this refined hotel is 1 km from Uhuru Park and 3 km from the Nairobi National Museum. Classy rooms provide free Wi-Fi, flat-screens, minibars, and balconies. Suites add lounges. There’s a bar, restaurant, and an outdoor pool surrounded by a sundeck.

hotels.name: The Boma Nairobi
hotels.description: Located near the Nairobi National Park, this upscale hotel features modern rooms with free Wi-Fi, minibars, flat-screen TVs, and room service. Amenities include a spa, gym, and restaurant with garden views.

hotels.name: Baobab Beach Resort & Spa
hotels.description: Nestled along the white sands of Diani Beach, this polished resort offers cozy rooms with ocean or garden views, plus dining, multiple pools, a spa, and entertainment. Perfect for a romantic getaway or family vacation.
